This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object detection in images. The use of FPN and deep learning models also suggests that it could belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The mention of edge devices and real-time processing suggests that it could also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Finally, the use of semi-supervised learning and knowledge distillation suggests that it could belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
